	(text "+5VPB			Platform Bus 5V1 	- 5A		(RPi)\n	> +3V3PB1 	Platform Bus 3V3 	- 2.5A		(PCIe)\n+VIMM			Interm. bus 3V8		- 1.2A\n	> +3V3PB2 	Platform Bus 3V3 	- 800mA		(ESP32, Switch)\n	> +3V3PB3 	Platform Bus 3V3 	- 300mA		(LoRa)\n	> +1V2PB  	Platform Bus 1V2	- 100mA		(Switch)\n\n+5VEXT1 External Bus 5V1			- 4A\n+5VEXT2 External Bus 5V				- 1.2A\n\n+3V3RPi RPi provided Bus 3V3		- 600mA\n\n+3V3SB 			Standby Bus 3V3		- ~0.1mA	(RPi RTC)"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 15.24 146.558 0)
		(effects
